flowchart TB
    UI[Compose UI] --> VM[ViewModels]
    VM --> REPO[Repositories]
    REPO --> DB[(Room DB)]
    REPO --> MESH[MeshNetworkManager]
    REPO --> GOSSIP[GossipSyncManager]
    GOSSIP --> CRDT[Delta Merge + Version Tracking]
    GOSSIP --> SEC[Encrypt + Compress Delta Envelope]
    MESH --> ROUTER[Hybrid Routing + Retry + TTL Relay]
    ROUTER --> TRANSPORT[Nearby / BLE / Wi-Fi Direct / LAN]
    ROUTER --> RELAY[Internet Relay/WebRTC Gateway]
    UI --> MINIAPP[WebView Mini App Engine]
    UI --> MAPS[Offline Map + POI]
    UI --> AI[Local AI Command Router]
